Hello! Welcome to your potion shop!
You're making potions for customers who want potions a specific way. They order either a Health, Mana or Stamina potion first. Click the fruits at the top to start making a potion, red for Health, blue for Mana, and green for Stamina.
Then they'll specify the exact flavor they want, in combinations of Sweet, Sour and Bitter in incredibly vague terms. Click and hold on the grapes to change the flavor of the potion. Purple for sweet, green for sour, and white for bitter.
Once it's full, you can click on the cauldron to serve and your customer will evaluate the potion.\
If you need a visual guide for your cauldron, click the eye button, and if you need to restart your potion click the trash button.
Good luck! Try to get five stars!
